Huan Zong?

00:20:32.282 --> 00:20:34.762
Kenapa muka awak merah sangat?

00:20:42.321 --> 00:20:44.442
Adakah awak marah

00:20:44.722 --> 00:20:46.242
sebab saya usik awak tadi?

